  "title": "Logistics Operations Specialist",
  "description": "<p>Stashworks Pte. Ltd. is a growing e-commerce fulfilment company.</p><p><br /></p><p>Our mission is to help SME grow and scale both domestically and internationally.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p>-Oversees a company's operational workflow, inventory inventory, equipment and people.</p><p><br /></p><p>-Resolve operational issues and disputes promptly or prevent it from even happening.</p><p><br /></p><p>-Maintain constant communication with managers, staff, and merchants to ensure proper operations of the company with brief summary to the Management.</p><p><br /></p><p>-Submit proposals or suggestions with supporting back up examples which can improve the workflow and increase profit margins within the organisation.</p><p><br /></p><p>-Develop, implement, and maintain quality assurance protocols, this includes a proper onboarding documentation process for all departments (Operational Handbook).</p><p><br /></p><p>-Increase the efficiency of existing processes and procedures to enhance the companys internal capacity.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Skills</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p>Overall responsible for the daily operations, including physical operations - receiving, storing, picking, packing, inventory management and worker-shift management.</p><p><br /></p><p>Meet warehouse operational SLA's by general management, problem-solving and employee coaching/training.</p><p><br /></p><p>On-site coordination with operations backend teams to ensure operational efficiency, safety and accuracy.</p><p><br /></p><p>Analysis of the data reports to identify performance bottleneck and improve the performance.</p><p><br /></p><p>Continuously improve the throughputs and attain a sustained level of delivery performance improvement.</p><p><br /></p><p>Strong Excel knowledge and passion to go above and beyond.</p><p><br /></p><p>Proficient in Management Skills Multi Tasking Warehousing will be better.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p># 5.5 work days per week, OT when necessary.</p><p><br /></p><p># Mondays to Fridays: 9:00 am to 6:00 pm, excluding Sundays and Public Holidays.</p><p><br /></p><p># Saturdays: 9:00 am to 1:00 pm.</p><p><br /></p><p># Easily accessible: 3 bus stops away from Joo Koon MRT Station/</p><p>bus-Interchange.</p><p><br /></p><p>#10 days Annual Leave.</p><p><br /></p><p># Condusive working enviornment.</p><p><br /></p><p># Team Bonus/es.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
